2017 Remuneration report (audited)

Introduction

The Transurban Board is pleased to present the Remuneration Report (Report) for the Transurban Group (‘Transurban' or the ‘Group’) for the year ended 30 June 2017 (‘FY17’), prepared in accordance with the Corporations Act 2001 (Cth) and the Corporations Regulations 2001 ((3th) This Report contains detailed

information regarding the remuneration arrangements for the Directors and senior executives who were key

management personnel (‘KMP’) of the Group during FY17.
